---

<Layout title="Home">
  <div class={styles.hero}>
    <h1 class={styles.heroTitle}>Tring Poker Club</h1>
    <p class={styles.heroSubtitle}>Every Wednesday 8pm Con Club, Â£10 buy in</p>
    <p class={styles.heroSubtitle}>ðŸ‘‹</p>
  </div>

  <section id="how-to-join" class={styles.contentSection}>
    <div class={styles.anchorOffset}></div>
    <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>How to Join Tring Poker Club</h2>
    <p>We play every Wednesday at 8pm at the Con Club, Tring.</p>
    <ul class={styles.infoList}>
      <li><strong>Location:</strong> 70 High St, Tring HP23 4AF</li>
      <li>
        <strong>Contact Email:</strong>
        <a href="mailto:tringpoker@gmail.com" class={styles.link}
          >tringpoker@gmail.com</a
        >
      </li>
      <li>Weâ€™re friendly and welcome beginnersâ€”come by early and play!</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      If you have any questions, feel free to email
      <code>tringpoker@gmail.com</code> or just drop by the Con Club on a Wednesday
      evening.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="how-to-play" class={styles.contentSection}>
    <div class={styles.anchorOffset}></div>
    <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>How to Play Poker</h2>
    <p>
      Below are the standard, basic poker rules we follow at Tring Poker Club.
      If youâ€™re new, arrive early and someone will guide you.
    </p>
    <h3 class={styles.subSectionTitle}>Basic Rules</h3>
    <ol class={styles.orderedList}>
      <li>
        <strong>Hand Rankings (highest to lowest):</strong>
        <ul class={styles.infoList}>
          <li>Royal Flush</li>
          <li>Straight Flush</li>
          <li>Four of a Kind</li>
          <li>Full House</li>
          <li>Flush</li>
          <li>Straight</li>
          <li>Three of a Kind</li>
          <li>Two Pair</li>
          <li>One Pair</li>
          <li>High Card</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Blinds:</strong> We use a small blind and big blind to encourage
        action.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Dealing:</strong> Each player receives two hole cards (face-down),
        then a round of betting.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>The Flop, Turn &amp; River:</strong>
        <ul class={styles.infoList}>
          <li>
            <em>Flop:</em> Three community cards are dealt face-up. Betting continues.
          </li>
          <li>
            <em>Turn:</em> A fourth community card is dealt face-up. Betting continues.
          </li>
          <li>
            <em>River:</em> A fifth community card is dealt face-up. Final betting
            round.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Showdown:</strong> If more than one player remains, the best five-card
        hand wins the pot.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class={styles.videoSection}>
    <div class={styles.videoWrapper}>
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CpSewSHZhmo"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
